@design_changes_since_original_snapshot
- Repo baseline repaired: GitHub main now has structured src/tests/docs layout.
- B1 live Scout harness added and merged to main.
- Greenhouse public host handling explicitly recognizes job-boards.greenhouse.io and boards.greenhouse.io.
- BoardRegistry now parses API URLs for Greenhouse, Lever, and Ashby instead of misreading path prefixes as handles.
- Compensation text parsing hardened:
  - interval detection uses salary-context window instead of entire job description.
  - European thousands like 110.000 normalize correctly.
  - implausibly large hourly parsed ranges are treated as annual.
- Placeholder OAuth docs added:
  - Privacy Policy
  - Support
  - Autonomy Contract
- Local OAuth implementation added without external NuGet packages.
- DPAPI token vault added for local OAuth token storage.
- Gmail live harness added.
- L1 Gmail labels deferred:
  - Earlier roadmap expected CareerSeeker label tree in B5.
  - Live testing showed label management is not available under gmail.compose alone.
  - Current design preserves scope minimalism: create drafts without custom labels in L1.
  - Label tree should be reconsidered only with explicit scope/CASA decision.
- client_secret*.json and token*.json added to .gitignore.
- Main branch now includes verified real Gmail draft creation.

